    </p>
    <p>Hallway walls are one of the best places to decorate. One can use murals as wall design. If murals seem like a lot of effort, you can make it into a photo gallery. When you search wall decor online you will find quite a few frames and styles that you can use to convert these walls into pretty walls. You can also make that space look larger with a lot of mirrors.</p>
    <p>
      <b>How to measure the wall when the door opens on that wall?</b>
    </p>
    <p>Ideally for wall art it is a rule to keep the door open and then measure the wall. The wall till where the knob reaches should be marked. Then the wall from that mark till the other end should be measured for using wall decor design. This makes sure your wall art fits perfectly and looks good. It doesn’t look offcentre.</p>
